{"tid":780331,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE MOMO 分享《2018 KCON LA》休息室","createTime":"2018-08-15T05:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T12:49:49.000Z","uid":51412,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"69835e88609c40b257f764ed29505a4c041e7e5c","tid":780331,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"TWICE MOMO 分享《2018 KCON LA》休息室照片，粉絲讚「好美」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bvHjeD3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbvHjeD3.png&h=abdec958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：TWICE@Instagram<br />\n<br />\nTWICE 在8月12日出席在美國洛杉磯舉辦的《KCON LA》，而 MOMO 也趁著空檔在<br />\n Instagram 上分享了幾張拿著紅花以及著裝完畢的全身照喔！<br />\n<br />\n照片中的 MOMO 拿著大、小不同的紅花在休息室中拍照，此外，她也在著裝完畢後分享了<br />\n全身照，身穿白色蕾絲小洋裝的 MOMO 真的很美呢！粉絲們也在看到照片後紛紛留言稱讚<br />\n「好美」、「好可愛」！<br />\n<br />\n來看看更多照片吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bfSNRT5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbfSNRT5.png&h=b4960892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/L64zw8u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FL64zw8u.png&h=4524d76b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FgjXJum.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFgjXJum.png&h=553b9b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jbcqo4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fjbcqo4a.png&h=f8cf80fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sjpIXhv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsjpIXhv.png&h=eb3016f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a8081712d657cc4a5b90b00717d9111ca0bf4db","tid":780331,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96634bc45587905f20a3f173cd5